'''Liberation Day''' was a [[holiday]] in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] that celebrated the [[Liberation of Coruscant (Galactic Civil War)|liberation]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was celebrated with massive fireworks on Coruscant.

